branchCategory.name: TU
branchCategory.description: <P>Series 10-TU tubing is a high quality, flexible, polyurethane tubing available for clean environments, with a particle generation of grade 1.  The minimum bending radius (value at which the tubing will fold at a temperature of 20 °C) ranges from 10mm to 35mm, depending on the model selected.  The 10-TU clean series is available in a 20m/roll length.  Available colors include: black, white, red, blue, yellow, green, clear and orange.</P>
